<descript>
<abstract>Commonwealth of Dominica, 1978 is a scanned map of the Caribbean country Commonwealth of Dominica at a scale of 1:25,000. The map is comprised with three sheets and georeferenced to the surface of the earth and fit to World Geodetic System (1984) coordinates. The original scanned file with additional information is also provided.</abstract>
<purpose>Scanned maps may be used for a variety of purposes. This image may be used in a GIS.</purpose>
</descript>
